const styles = {

      border:0,

      justifyContent: "space-between",
      alignItems: "center"

    },

  checkBox:{

  },
  liContent :{
    fontFamily: 'Josefin Sans',
  fontSize: '12px',
  fontWeight: '400',

  letterSpacing: '-0.1666666716337204px',

  color:'#9495A5'
  },
  liContentChecked :{
    fontFamily: 'Josefin Sans',

  color:'#D1D2DA',
  textDecoration: 'line-through'
  }
}
  

  export default styles;
